works.description: The hotly awaited Carte Blanche, the new James Bond book by top American thriller writer Jeffery Deaver, is out now in the UK, Ireland, Australia, New Zealand, Italy, The Netherlands, Russia and Korea. The first copies of the new Bond book, published by Hodder & Stoughton, were launched in a unique and stylish way at St. Pancras International in London. At the high profile event was a luxury car, champagne on tap, Royal Marines Commandos abseiling and a beautiful Bond girl on a vintage motorbike.
